Introduction

Lee Nagyung is a South Korean singer-songwriter, actress, dancer, and composer under ASND. She was one of the lead vocalists and visuals of the girl group fromis_9.

Nagyung was born in Korea but had to move and study in China when she was younger. In 2017, she appeared and competed in the show "Idol School" where she ranked 5th with 64,001 votes, earning her a spot in the group.

Nagyung debuted as a member of fromis_9 on January 24, 2018, with the mini album To. Heart.

On October 2021, Nagyung made her acting debut in the popular K-drama "Shadow Beauty".
